qtweather (0.7.10) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed bug with the dialog showing on screens that don't belong to QtWeather
  * Efficiency tweaks
  * Corrected weather service title: from NAOO to NOAA
  * Changed the download location of the XML file to my own server. 
    This allowed me to create a much more logical and organized layout 
    to parse, with less code in the application
  * Eliminated the temporary file

